Umar Farouk Abdulmutallab was
sentenced to life in prison for attempting to bomb a Northwest
Airlines plane on Christmas Day 2009 with explosives hidden in
his underwear.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Margaret Cronin Fisk in Detroit at 
 mcfisk@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
